  <original-body>When using STI, a Uninitialised Constant error is thrown when calling subclasses (Doc in following example) before parent class is called (container in following example).

Ex:
@@@ Ruby
class Container &lt; ActiveRecord::Base
end

class Doc &lt; Container
end

Doc
#=&gt; uninitialized constant Doc
Container
#=&gt; Okay
Doc
#=&gt; Okay</original-body>
